  "text": "Is there anything that we can specifically do to alleviate the problem that is already existing? I am Ra. This information is harmless, thus we share it though it is transient, lacking the principle but only offering a specific transient effect. The wrist area should be wrapped as in the sprained configuration, as you call this distortion, and what you call a sling may be used on this distorted right side of the body complex for one diurnal period. At that time symptoms, as you call these distortions, shall be reviewed and such repeated until the distortion is alleviated. The healing work to which each is apprentice may be used as desired. It is to be noted that a crystal is available.",
